Disneyland Tours
Air California flies you
directly to Orange County
Airport, only minutes away
from The Magic Kingdom.
The Disneyland Tour
includes: two nights at one
of the hotels listed. Trans-
portation from Orange
County Airport direct to the
Grand Hotel or Disneyland
Hotel (Anaheim Hyatt House
provides transfers from
Grand Hotel). Entrance to
Disneyland and book of ten
rides.
Exciting Tour Options
Lion Country Safari. This
fantastic Game Reserve
transports you to deepest
Africa. See the world's largest
collection of lions and other
African wildlife from your
own rental car. Only a short
distance from Disneyland.
Marineland Of The
Pacific. Tour leaves daily
from your hotel, visiting Seal
Beach, Long Beach including
the harbor and Naval Base,
Los Angeles Harbor over the

Other Attractions
Within a few minutes
drive of your hotel are
Knott's Berry Farm, where
you can spend the entire day
in a charming America of
yesteryear, the new $20
million Anaheim Stadium,
home of the California
Angels, Movieland Wax
Museum, Japanese Village
and Deer Park, Movieland of
the Air, Mission San Juan
Capistrano.
Rent-A-Car Service
Car rentals for two or
more persons are available
as part of the Disneyland
Tour package and in place of
transfer service. Special rates
available on request.
